Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.98,0:00:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.54,0:00:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for calling on you so early.\NI'm from the state police.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.31,0:00:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you Dr. Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.15,0:00:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What can I do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.55,0:00:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, but were you at home\Nall night?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.39,0:00:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No... I was out drinking\Nuntil it was nearly morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.86,0:00:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.90,0:00:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.93,0:00:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Eisler Memorial Hospital's\NDirector Heinemann;
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.53,0:00:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief of Surgery, Dr. Oppenheim,\Nand Dr. Boyer are dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.83,0:02:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, no one except the police\Nare allowed at the scene of the crime!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.57,0:02:26.04,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(750,750)\pos(360,340)}A Murder
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.57,0:02:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, you are obstructing\Nthe operations of the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.04,0:02:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The Press is not allowed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.14,0:02:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- inside the hospital!\N- Please don't do anything
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.27,0:02:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,to excite the patients!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.11,0:02:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it an accident?\NOr was it murder?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.64,0:02:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Three people died at the same time!\NOf course it was murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.51,0:02:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you from the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.98,0:02:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know anything\Nabout this incident?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.68,0:02:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of my way!\NLet me through!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.15,0:02:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! No one is allowed in!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.82,0:02:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Dr. Kenzo Tenma of this hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.06,0:02:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... go right ahead.\NHey! Don't push!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.63,0:02:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So, did you see anyone suspicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.23,0:02:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.\NNow is not the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.36,0:02:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- Now is not the time...\N- Dr. Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.67,0:02:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma! The Director!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.67,0:02:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.74,0:03:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, calm down!\NAre the emergencies taken care of?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.74,0:03:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well, even at this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.34,0:03:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,there's been no end\Nto the emergencies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.84,0:03:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,There are two patients\Nwaiting to be operated on...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.78,0:03:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand. I'll help out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.11,0:03:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of the car accident victim\Nwith the brain contusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.08,0:03:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go to the X-ray Reading Room\Nto look at the x-rays first.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.15,0:03:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the other case?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.32,0:03:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,A patient who collapsed due to a stroke.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.19,0:03:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Doctor, will you help us\Nin our investigation?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.76,0:03:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Now is not the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.36,0:03:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that,\Nbut the initial investigation is vital!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.50,0:03:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know of anyone with a grudge\Nagainst the director and the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.87,0:03:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,A grudge?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.27,0:03:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You may consider your path\Nto becoming
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.20,0:03:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the doctor you envisioned closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.68,0:03:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Do you know something?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.41,0:03:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.58,0:03:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.92,0:03:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Trouble! Those kids...\NThe twin brother and sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.99,0:03:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't find them anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.87,0:04:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the sister's bed empty, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.67,0:04:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I looked!\NBut they're nowhere to be found...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.07,0:04:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.11,0:04:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What in the world has happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.55,0:04:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,...compassionately extended\Na helping hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.92,0:04:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We will surely praise his lifetime\Nof achievements through eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.99,0:04:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Farewell Dr. Heinemann.\NRest in peace. Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.00,0:04:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.24,0:04:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- Eva...\N- Eva.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.24,0:04:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's difficult,\Nbut pull yourself together...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.05,0:04:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.45,0:04:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Give back my father!\NFather!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.56,0:05:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just too much, Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.30,0:05:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.56,0:05:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Up until now, she lived an easy life\Nas the director's daughter...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.17,0:05:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Now suddenly,\Nshe's just an ordinary person.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.37,0:05:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be a big shock...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.07,0:05:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you say that\Nat a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.08,0:05:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.68,0:05:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Dr. Tenma, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.61,0:05:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Detective Visbaugh
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.05,0:05:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,of the Nordhein-Westfalen\NPolice Department.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.92,0:05:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your efforts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.39,0:05:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This was such a tragic incident...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.09,0:05:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.39,0:05:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me introduce you. This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.73,0:05:38.31,Names,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,0)\fs16}German Federal Criminal Police Office [BKA]\N{\fs24}Inspector Lunge
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.42,0:05:38.09,Default,,0,0,120,,I am Inspector Lunge of the BKA.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.00,0:05:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard rumors that\Nyou are a brilliant physician.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.60,0:05:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all. I've still got\Na long ways to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.77,0:05:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Have you any idea\Nwhere the children are?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.91,0:05:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.94,0:05:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We have determined what caused
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.31,0:05:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,the death of the director\Nand the other two.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.51,0:06:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We found a nitrate type poison\Nin their bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.89,0:06:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Nitrates...\NThat means a muscular relaxant...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.62,0:06:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,As expected of a doctor.\NYou are knowledgeable...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.23,0:06:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But how could something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.49,0:06:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It was candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.43,0:06:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Candy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.56,0:06:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The same candy wrapper\Nwas found beside each body,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.24,0:06:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and the same candy was found\Nin their stomachs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.64,0:06:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.67,0:06:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you have any idea\Nwhere the three of them
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.78,0:06:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,might get a hold of\Nsomething like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.25,0:06:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know anything about that.\NWhat about the search for the twins?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.32,0:06:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The BKA has\Ntaken over the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.69,0:06:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.29,0:06:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This incident may have started
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.49,0:06:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,when the parents of those twins\Nwere shot and killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.47,0:06:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Their parents defected\Nfrom East Germany
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.23,0:06:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and were killed by someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.17,0:06:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, the director and doctors\Nof the hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.00,0:06:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,where the children were taken to\Nwere killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.11,0:06:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,There is also the possibility\Nthat this is political terrorism.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.41,0:07:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Those children might be\Nholding a major clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.35,0:07:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.\NPlease find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.68,0:07:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We will do our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.55,0:07:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.56,0:07:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Before the incident, the Director\Nremoved him from his position as Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.83,0:07:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, the Director's daughter\Nbroke off her engagement to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.40,0:07:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But he was in a bar drinking\Nat the time of the incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.84,0:07:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He has an alibi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.61,0:07:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm...\NMay I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.31,0:07:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you move\Nyour hand like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.28,0:07:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?\NOh, I'm typing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.18,0:07:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.65,0:07:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm inputting all the information into\Nthe disk in my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.62,0:07:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,When I press the key\Nto extract the information...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.46,0:07:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,"Not at all. I still have\Na long ways to go."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.89,0:07:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what Dr. Tenma bashfully said\Nwhen I called him brilliant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.20,0:08:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The police? Do they suspect you\Nof doing something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.11,0:08:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because there's enough evidence\Nfor me to be a suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.68,0:08:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.05,0:08:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They were quite persistent\Nwhen they questioned me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.55,0:08:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm exhausted...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.82,0:08:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,When the dust from this thing settles,\NI think I'll go back to Japan...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.29,0:08:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- What?\N- I came to Germany to do research,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.33,0:08:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,but due to the recent chain of events,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.20,0:08:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I've gone back to saving lives,\Nthe true duty of a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.90,0:08:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't be so depressing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.21,0:08:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm tired...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.54,0:08:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just so tired...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.38,0:08:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Your progress is favorable,\NMr. Buchner.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.82,0:08:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Dr. Tenma.\NDo you think I can work again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.42,0:08:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.13,0:08:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,My store will go under\Nif I'm not there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.06,0:09:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But you mustn't overdo it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.63,0:09:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go have a drink there\Nafter you're released.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.17,0:09:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be there to make sure\Nyou don't overdo things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.70,0:09:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.17,0:09:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.24,0:09:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that you were\Nleaving this hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.78,0:09:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.31,0:09:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.78,0:09:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.08,0:09:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There aren't any\Ngood doctors like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.89,0:09:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't say you're quitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.69,0:09:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.96,0:09:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Buchner...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.53,0:09:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma, the Chairman\Nis asking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.70,0:09:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The board is discussing who should\Nsucceed to the empty posts.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.44,0:09:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Up until now, the Director's faction\Nhas filled the major positions...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.28,0:09:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There will be a considerable\Npurging of personnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.05,0:09:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The rumor is Dr. Eckner\Nis being transferred
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.62,0:09:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,to a small hospital in Bavaria.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.22,0:09:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- Is that so...\N- Umm, Dr. Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.22,0:10:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- Huh?\N- No matter what the Chairman says,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.46,0:10:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,please don't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.66,0:10:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.13,0:10:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't leave this hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.60,0:10:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.97,0:10:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll say it again.\NI am performance oriented.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.91,0:10:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma, you are appointed to\NChief of Surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.45,0:10:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What a life...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.06,0:10:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I went against the orders\Nof the Director,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.23,0:10:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}lost my position as Chief,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.03,0:10:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and my engagement to Eva\Nwas dissolved.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.73,0:10:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As soon as I decide to work\Nas a simple doctor
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.40,0:10:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}without any hope of promotion...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.98,0:10:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What a life!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.69,0:11:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for calling you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.99,0:11:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you've been appointed\NChief of Surgery. That's very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.93,0:11:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.67,0:11:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenzo... At my father's funeral,\Nyou tried to comfort me, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.07,0:11:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.81,0:11:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It made me happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.48,0:11:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of things happened between us,\Nbut I'd like to try again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.69,0:11:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenzo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.46,0:11:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenzo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.16,0:11:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! I was wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.93,0:11:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to try again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.04,0:11:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenzo...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.01,0:11:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenzo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.78,0:12:06.95,Titles1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\an8}9 Years Later
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.95,0:12:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The patient hospitalized\Nfor a spinal cord tumor...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.28,0:12:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,His paralysis has accelerated.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.45,0:12:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.\NI'll perform the operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.32,0:12:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If you will, Chief of Surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.76,0:12:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Make the arrangements\Nfor the operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.66,0:12:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.64,0:12:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, when will this flood recede?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.97,0:12:31.68,Titles1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(750,750)\an8}1995\NKöln,\N(Germany)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.31,0:12:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought the world would change
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.55,0:12:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,when the Berlin Wall came down\Nsix years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.68,0:12:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,but nothing good has happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.78,0:12:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Even with the unification of Europe,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.69,0:12:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,hopeless people from all over\Ncome flowing in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.82,0:12:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. There's been an increase in\Nunexplainable crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.69,0:12:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.06,0:12:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector, we've arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.53,0:12:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Both victims had their throats\Nslit open with a knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.07,0:12:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Their identities?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.30,0:12:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The Reichmanns of Stich Drive
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.04,0:12:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,They were murdered in their home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.61,0:13:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We believe that they were\Nhidden in a closet,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.88,0:13:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and their bodies floated out\Nbecause of the flood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.72,0:13:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,A murder of a middle-aged couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.29,0:13:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,There have been four incidents\Nin Germany
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.92,0:13:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,over the past two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.49,0:13:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,All by the same method.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.39,0:13:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's probably a robber who targets\Nrich middle-aged couples.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.56,0:13:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's too soon\Nto call them robberies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.90,0:13:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,According to the data,\Nfor some reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.83,0:13:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,all of the couples\Ndid not have children.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.67,0:13:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This couple certainly\Ndid not have any children.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.67,0:13:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think there are\Ntoo many similarities
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.14,0:13:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,to call them robberies?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.28,0:13:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But money and goods have been\Ntaken from all of the victims' homes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.72,0:13:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,All of them totaling very little.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.42,0:13:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It would make sense\Nif a single perpetrator did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.82,0:13:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you suggesting that\Nthere wasn't a single perpetrator?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.69,0:13:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Two of the homes had\Nextremely strong locks and alarms.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.63,0:13:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But the perpetrator opened them\Nand entered very easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.97,0:14:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, all the couples did not seem to\Nfight back when they were killed
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.77,0:14:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and the neighbors did not hear\Nany noise at the time of the incidents.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.04,0:14:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think they were\Ntoo skillfully done
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.68,0:14:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,for it to have been done by\Na single individual?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.98,0:14:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know this man?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.75,0:14:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.78,0:14:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Adolph Junkers, 32 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.42,0:14:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He has been convicted twice\Nfor larceny.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.39,0:14:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,His role was to open locks...\NIn other words, he's a lock picker.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.79,0:14:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He was seen near the scene
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.56,0:14:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,of three of the murders\Nof middle-aged couples.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.60,0:14:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Then did this man do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.14,0:14:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't say.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.81,0:14:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's the extent\Nof your work as state police.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.41,0:14:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave the rest to the BKA.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.38,0:14:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.29,0:14:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.32,0:14:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It didn't fly after all.\NI've never flown a kite before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.76,0:14:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It almost went up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.53,0:14:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, how was the girl last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.46,0:15:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,How was she?\NShe was a nice person.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.23,0:15:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, she's the daughter\Nof a director, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.47,0:15:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you just had dinner\Nand saw her home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.04,0:15:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there was an emergency call\Nduring dinner,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.07,0:15:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,so I had to come back to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.84,0:15:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?! You'd better rethink that\Nall work and no play doctrine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.18,0:15:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to lose a great catch\Nand regret it some day!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.45,0:15:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Are you listening,\NChief of Surgery?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.45,0:15:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,A kite?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.56,0:15:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.46,0:15:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that yours, Karl?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.96,0:15:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,My grandpa gave it to me,\Nbut it just won't fly...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.23,0:15:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be it's unbalanced?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.60,0:15:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief, can you fly a kite?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.40,0:15:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it often during my childhood in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.51,0:15:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Try holding it up high, Karl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.44,0:15:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.81,0:15:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.\NNow... will it work?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.68,0:15:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- Heave ho!\N- There!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.95,0:15:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- There we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.50,0:16:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.63,0:16:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.44,0:16:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.87,0:16:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were in his shoes,\NI'd have at least five lovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.68,0:16:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.94,0:16:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's amazing, Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.18,0:16:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Get well quickly\Nand fly it yourself, Karl.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.28,0:16:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.29,0:16:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's surgery is\Na parasellar meningioma extirpation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.70,0:16:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll proceed with\Na right pterional approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.93,0:16:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.13,0:16:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch closely. Chief Tenma\Nwill perform the surgery himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.57,0:16:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What a splendid operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.54,0:16:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He's hardly retracted the brain at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.14,0:16:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He truly is a surgical genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.65,0:16:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You residents should treat the brain\Nwith tender care.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.02,0:17:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Always keep this in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.87,0:17:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.79,0:17:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This is terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.82,0:17:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- Look at the blood!\N- Ambulance! Call an ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.96,0:17:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I didn't do it!\NIt's not my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.70,0:17:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This man ran into the street suddenly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.70,0:17:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the patient?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.07,0:17:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.21,0:17:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,How is his condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.24,0:18:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I can't say...\NThere's nothing more we can do...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.61,0:18:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a material witness\Nin a certain case.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.41,0:18:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,His testimony alone\Ncould solve a serial murder case.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.59,0:18:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't have him die.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.16,0:18:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But the patient is\Nin a very critical condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.33,0:18:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing more can be done\Nat our hospital...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.30,0:18:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a terrific brain surgeon\Nat Eisler Memorial Hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.40,0:18:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If he came...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.50,0:18:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Brain surgeon...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.87,0:18:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean Dr. Tenma...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.91,0:18:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming all this way,\NDr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.55,0:18:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,How is the patient's condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.45,0:18:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He is in a coma.\NAnd one of his pupils is dilated.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.65,0:18:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a long time, Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.62,0:18:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... I'm sorry,\Nbut who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.93,0:18:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been nine years.\NNot since the Director's funeral...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.97,0:18:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm not mistaken,\Nyou're with the BKA.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.03,0:18:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector Lunge.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.74,0:19:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Please make this operation a success\Nfor the sake of the BKA.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.91,0:19:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.04,0:19:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The patient has to live.\NHe holds the key to solving a big case.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.05,0:19:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't operate\Nfor the sake of the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.95,0:19:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I do it for the sake of the patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.59,0:19:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.06,0:19:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I have an operation to perform...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.59,0:19:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear you've become\Nthe Chief of Surgery, Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.03,0:19:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been very successful...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.90,0:19:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.37,0:19:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No. At your age,\Nit's quite an accomplishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.87,0:19:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you in line\Nto become the next Director?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.71,0:19:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that would be\Na long way off for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.81,0:19:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,About the murders\Nat the Eisler Memorial Hospital...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.78,0:19:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,There is very little evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.05,0:19:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The investigation\Nhas been extremely difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.45,0:19:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The only clue is the poisoned candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.45,0:19:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The methodology means\Nit is an intelligent crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.26,0:19:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,An intelligent crime means
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.03,0:20:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,the victim and the assailant\Nhave some sort of interests at stake
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.03,0:20:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.87,0:20:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No, excuse me. In this business,\NI'm constantly thinking like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.61,0:20:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, rest assured.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.71,0:20:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,All the cases I've ever handled\Nhave been solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.01,0:20:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Every single one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.58,0:20:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.63,0:20:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We will perform a craniotomy\Nto remove the hematoma.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.60,0:20:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We must hurry. There is the danger\Nof the brain hernia worsening.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.57,0:20:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how you look at it,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.67,0:20:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,only one person greatly benefited from\Nthe Eisler Memorial Hospital murders.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.01,0:20:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That is you, Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.46,0:21:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for taking the trouble\Nto come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.66,0:21:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all. How has\Nthe patient been doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.56,0:21:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He's conscious,\Nbut his right pupil remains dilated...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.53,0:21:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And he has some paralysis\Non the left side.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.70,0:21:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He's started rehab already, hasn't he?\NThe paralysis should go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.47,0:21:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He's recovering normally.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.87,0:21:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, the police will want to see him,\Nbut please refuse for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.41,0:21:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But, that detective, Lunge,\Nis so persistent...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.32,0:21:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, the patient's recovery\Nis most important.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.93,0:21:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you feeling, Mr. Junkers?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.63,0:21:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Junkers, do you recognize me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.47,0:21:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you see this finger?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.81,0:21:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,How about it? Can you answer me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.65,0:21:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.12,0:22:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The monster... is coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.52,0:22:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that, Mr. Junkers?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.12,0:22:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The monster... is coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.93,0:22:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming? What's coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.63,0:22:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The monster is coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.97,0:22:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The monster... is coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.77,0:22:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The monster?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.07,0:23:53.53,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)\pos(360,340)}Night of the Execution
